(Okay, the great one - me - shall post some today and much tomorrow.  Well, 
possibly.  I'm going to try and see Rock Star tomorrow.  Why?  That's a good 
question.

Just a reminder to all, Rock Star starts tomorrow, Friday, September 7th. It 
stars Mark Wahlberg as a heavy metal fan that becomes the lead singer for his 
favorite metal band, Steel Dragon, and Jennifer Aniston is his hot girlfriend.

Its soundtrack includes Bon Jovi, Def Leppard, Motley Crue, and Sammy Hagar 
(the CD soundtrack doesn't have Def Leppard's "Animal" though :(, so after 
hearing those four names you know you have to go TO the theatres and WATCH 
this movie. Then go TO a store and BUY the soundtrack. It has a member of 
Dokken in it for crying out loud, and you aren't at the theatres yet!? Go go 
go go! I guarantee this movie will not suck, if it does I'll let you take 
shots at me with a baseball bat.

-Unitron

Seriously, see the movie, with an awesome soundtrack and a great actor like 
Wahlberg, it won't, nay, can't dissapoint. )
